{"title":"记账不再划××","authors":["宁凤"],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":10,"day":18}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"记账不再划××"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小队员，回了家，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"帮助妈妈学文化。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"左一撇，右一划，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大娘认识洋字码。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"1字像粉笔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"2字像只鸭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"3字像耳朵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"4字像犁铧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"5字像秤钩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"6字像豆芽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"7字像镰刀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"8字像麻花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"9字像饭勺，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"0字像西瓜。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"学会字码心高兴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"记账不再划××。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宁　凤"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}